O is one of the best marketing channels you can use to reach your target audience and market your brand and products. For one, it’s one of&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-marketing-tools/\">20+ Best SEO Marketing Tools to Drive Traffic and Revenue in 2024</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70875:\"<p>Looking for the best SEO marketing tools to help drive traffic and revenue?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO is one of the best marketing channels you can use to reach your target audience and market your brand and products. For one, it’s one of the cheapest marketing channels, enabling you to generate <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/organic-traffic/\" title=\"What is Organic Traffic? [9+ Tips to Increase it on Your Site]\">organic traffic</a> and leads. Plus, most online searches start with a search engine, making SEO marketing a critical part of every digital marketing strategy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you some of the best SEO marketing tools for driving traffic and revenue online.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-seo-marketing-tools\">What are SEO Marketing Tools?</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-benefits-of-using-seo-marketing-tools\">Benefits of Using SEO Marketing Tools</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-20-best-seo-marketing-tools-expert-picks\">20+ Best SEO Marketing Tools: Expert Picks</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-broken-link-checker\">2. Broken Link Checker</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-wpforms\">3. WPForms</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-seo-analyzer-by-aioseo\">3. SEO Analyzer by AIOSEO</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-optinmonster\">4. OptinMonster</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-semrush\">5. Semrush</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-6-monsterinsights\">6. MonsterInsights</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-7-affiliatewp\">7. AffiliateWP</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-8-ahrefs\">8. Ahrefs</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-9-pushengage\">9. PushEngage</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-10-trustpulse\">10. TrustPulse</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-11-funnelkit-formerly-woofunnels\">11. FunnelKit (formerly WooFunnels)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-12-google-search-console\">12. Google Search Console</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-13-instagram-feed-pro\">13. Instagram Feed Pro</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-14-google-trends\">14. Google Trends</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-15-easy-digital-downloads-edd\">15. Easy Digital Downloads (EDD)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-16-facebook-social-post-feed\">16. Facebook Feed Pro</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-17-thrive-leads\">17. Thrive Leads</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-18-exploding-topics\">18. Exploding Topics</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-19-rafflepress\">19. RafflePress</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-20-google-keyword-planner\">20. Google Keyword Planner</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-21-feeds-for-youtube\">21. Feeds for YouTube</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-22-advanced-coupons\">22. Advanced Coupons</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-23-easy-affiliate\">23. Easy Affiliate</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-24-pretty-links\">24. Pretty Links</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-25-thirstyaffiliates\">25. ThirstyAffiliates</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-seo-marketing-tools-your-faqs-answered\">SEO Marketing Tools: Your FAQs Answered</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-seo-marketing-tools\">What are SEO Marketing Tools?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-the-different-types-of-seo-marketing-tools\">What are the different types of SEO marketing tools?</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-what-are-the-best-seo-marketing-tools\">What are the best SEO marketing tools?</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-best-seo-marketing-tools-our-top-picks\">Best SEO Marketing Tools: Our Top Picks</a></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-what-are-seo-marketing-tools\">What are SEO Marketing Tools?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>SEO marketing tools are software applications designed to assist businesses in optimizing their websites for better search engine visibility, traffic, and revenue generation. These tools offer a wide range of features, including:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/keyword-research/\" title=\"Keyword Research for SEO: An In-Depth Beginner’s Guide\">Keyword research</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/on-page-seo/\" title=\"On-Page SEO: Complete Guide for Beginners\">On-page optimization</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/technical-seo/\" title=\"What Is Technical SEO? The Best Checklist in 2024\">Technical SEO</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/link-building-guide/\" title=\"The Ultimate Link Building Guide You Need for 2024\">Link building</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-perform-website-seo-analysis-on-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Perform an SEO Analysis on Your WordPress Website\">SEO analysis</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-do-an-seo-competitor-analysis/\" title=\"How to Do an SEO Competitor Analysis [The Easy Way]\">Competitor analysis</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>By leveraging these tools, you can streamline your SEO efforts and stay ahead of the competition.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-benefits-of-using-seo-marketing-tools\">Benefits of Using SEO Marketing Tools</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are several reasons why you should use SEO marketing tools to help your business grow. Some of the common ones include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Time and resource efficiency</strong>: SEO marketing tools automate many tasks, saving you valuable time and resources that would otherwise be spent on manual processes.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Improved search rankings</strong>: SEO marketing tools help you identify ranking opportunities, increasing their chances of ranking higher in <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-serps/\" title=\"What Are SERPs (And Why Are they Important to SEO)?\">search engine results pages</a> (SERPs).</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Increased organic traffic</strong>: You can attract more relevant visitors by optimizing your site for search engines, resulting in more leads and sales.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Competitor analysis</strong>: Many SEO marketing tools offer features that allow you to analyze your competitors\' strategies, strengths, and weaknesses, enabling you to stay ahead of the competition.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Data-driven insights</strong>: SEO marketing tools provide you with comprehensive data and analytics, enabling them to make informed decisions and continuously optimize their strategies.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to run impactful digital marketing campaigns, you definitely need some SEO marketing tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-20-best-seo-marketing-tools-expert-picks\">20+ Best SEO Marketing Tools: Expert Picks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to equip yourself or your team with the best SEO marketing tools?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s quickly dive into our expertly curated list</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"All in One SEO - WordPress SEO Plugin and Toolkit\" rel=\"noopener\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO)</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png\" alt=\"AIOSEO is a powerful SEO marketing tool that can help you boost your search visibility.\" class=\"wp-image-151544\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"All in One SEO - WordPress SEO Plugin and Toolkit\" rel=\"noopener\">AIOSEO</a> is the best SEO marketing tool you can have in your toolbox. It’s a powerful yet easy-to-use SEO plugin that boasts over 3 million active users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Millions of smart business owners use AIOSEO to boost their search engine rankings and drive qualified traffic to their WordPress sites. Remember, to achieve your business goals, you need to drive organic traffic to your site. AIOSEO has many powerful SEO features and modules to help you do that.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The plugin even has features designed specifically for <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\" title=\"Ultimate WordPress SEO Guide: Optimize Your Site in 2024\">WordPress SEO</a>. It lets you optimize your posts and pages for greater visibility on search engines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Examples of SEO features that can help you boost your online visibility include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-cornerstone-content/\" title=\"What is Cornerstone Content? Plus Tips and Examples\">Cornerstone Content</a></strong>: Helps you build topical authority and enhances your semantic SEO.&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/search-statistics/\" title=\"Search Statistics\">Search Statistics</a></strong>: This powerful Google Search Console integration lets you track your keyword rankings and see important SEO metrics with 1-click, and more.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/robots-editor/\" title=\"Robots.txt Editor\">Advanced Robots.txt Generator</a></strong>: Easily generate and customize your robots.txt file for better crawling and indexing.&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-aioseo-4-2-5-next-gen-schema-generator-to-improve-your-seo-rankings/\" title=\"Announcing AIOSEO 4.2.5: Next-Gen Schema Generator to Improve Your SEO Rankings\">Next-gen Schema generator</a></strong>: This no-code schema generator enables users to generate and output any schema markup on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/redirection-manager/\" title=\"Redirection Manager\">Redirection Manager</a></strong>: Helps you manage redirects and eliminate 404 errors, making it easier for search engines to crawl and index your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/smart-xml-sitemaps/\" title=\"Smart XML Sitemaps\">Sitemap generator</a></strong>: Automatically generate different types of sitemaps to notify all search engines of any updates on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\" title=\"Features\">And more</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The SEO modules in AIOSEO are super easy to use and designed to give your website and content a better chance of ranking. If you run an eCommerce store built on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/woocommerce/\" title=\"WooCommerce\">WooCommerce</a>, AIOSEO has features built to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/woocommerce-seo/\" title=\"WooCommerce SEO\">help your product pages rank</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, AIOSEO also has modules to help with <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/local-seo/\" title=\"Local SEO: What it is and How to Ace it: (WordPress Beginners Guide)\">local SEO</a>, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/on-page-seo/\" title=\"On-Page SEO: Complete Guide for Beginners\">on-page SEO</a>, and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/technical-seo/\" title=\"What Is Technical SEO? The Best Checklist in 2024\">technical SEO</a>. All these features make AIOSEO one of the best SEO marketing tools for WordPress users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">detailed installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $49.60. A free plan is also available.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-2-broken-link-checker\">2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/broken-link-checker\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Broken Link Checker by AIOSEO\" rel=\"noopener\">Broken Link Checker</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/broken-link-checker\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"325\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/best-wordpress-plugins-broken-link-checker.png\" alt=\"Fixing broken links helps improve crawlability.\" class=\"wp-image-225760\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/best-wordpress-plugins-broken-link-checker.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/best-wordpress-plugins-broken-link-checker-300x139.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/best-wordpress-plugins-broken-link-checker-600x278.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/broken-link-checker\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Broken Link Checker by AIOSEO\" rel=\"noopener\">Broken Link Checker</a> (BLC) is another <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-plugins/\" title=\"32 Best WordPress Plugins in 2024 [Paid and Free]\">WordPress plugin</a> that should be high on your list of SEO marketing tools. Developed by the team behind the All In One SEO (AIOSEO) plugin, you can be confident the code is clean and the plugin effective.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Links are among the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/google-ranking-factors/\" title=\"10 Google Ranking Factors to Act on in 2024\">top ranking factors</a> search engines use to rank content. Any broken links on your site can hinder crawling and indexing, costing you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Traffic</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rankings</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Conversions</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s why your SEO marketing plan must include checking for broken links. And this is where BLC comes in.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Broken Link Checker, you can easily find and fix broken links on your site, both internal and external. The best part is that the plugin automates the entire process! This saves you a lot of time, as you won’t have to manually look for and test all the broken links on your site. When you find a broken link, you can edit the URL, unlink it, recheck it, or redirect it!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Broken Link Checker is undoubtedly one of the first SEO marketing tools you should install on your site if you’re serious about your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-check-site-health/\" title=\"How to Check Site Health for Your WordPress Website\">site’s health</a> and SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free. Paid plans start at $4.99.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-3-wpforms\">3. <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPForms - Drag & Drop WordPress Form Builder\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"435\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/best-wordpress-multisite-plugins-wpforms.png\" alt=\"WPForms home page.\" class=\"wp-image-128844\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/best-wordpress-multisite-plugins-wpforms.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/best-wordpress-multisite-plugins-wpforms-300x186.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/best-wordpress-multisite-plugins-wpforms-600x373.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Lead generation is a critical component of successful SEO marketing. And this is where a WordPress plugin like <a href=\"https://wpforms.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WPForms - Drag & Drop WordPress Form Builder\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a> comes into play.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WPForms is the best contact form plugin for WordPress. It helps users capture visitor information without adding friction to the user experience (UX). Plus, it’s easy to install and deploy on your site thanks to the user-friendly drag-and-drop builder functionality and over 700 pre-built form templates. This makes it an excellent SEO marketing tool for one-man marketing teams.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With WPForms on your site, you can easily create:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Contact forms</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Email subscription forms</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Online order forms</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Payment forms</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Surveys and polls</li>\n\n\n\n<li>And more</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The best part is that you can create professional-looking forms with just a few clicks.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WPForms also integrates with the most popular payment platforms like Stripe, PayPal, Square, and Authorize.net. This makes it easy to build forms with a payment feature. And all this can be done in less than 5 minutes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WPForms has advanced features you won’t find in other form builders. Examples include conversational forms, lead forms, form landing pages, user journey tracking, form abandonment, geolocation tracking, GDPR-friendly, custom WordPress user registration and login forms, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If lead generation is a marketing priority, consider installing WPForms to your WordPress site ASAP!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free. Paid plans start at $49.50/year</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-3-seo-analyzer-by-aioseo\">3. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-analyzer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"SEO Analyzer by AIOSEO\">SEO Analyzer by AIOSEO</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1002\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-analyzer-1.png\" alt=\"SEO Analyzer by AIOSEO\" class=\"wp-image-365228\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-analyzer-1.png 1002w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-analyzer-1-300x128.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-analyzer-1-768x327.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-analyzer-1-600x255.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Another must-have SEO marketing tool to include in your marketing toolbox is AIOSEO’s <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-analyzer/\" title=\"SEO Analyzer by SEO\">SEO Analyzer</a>. This powerful tool crawls and audits your site to detect critical errors. It also gives you actionable insights to help you improve your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In essence, SEO Analyzer acts like your personal SEO checkup, identifying areas where your website might be lagging and offering solutions to boost your ranking. Examples of how AIOSEO\'s analyzer helps you implement <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-best-practices/\" title=\"SEO Best Practices: 20+ Proven Tips to Boost Your Search Rankings\">SEO best practices</a> include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Find SEO issues</strong>: Easily find SEO-related issues on your website and get actionable data to fix them before they become a problem.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Fix critical issues</strong>: Overhaul your website and get rid of all SEO issues negatively impacting your site.&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Free SEO report</strong>: Get a detailed report for your website. See where your SEO is working and where it needs improvement.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides analyzing your site, you can use SEO Analyzer to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-do-an-seo-competitor-analysis/\" title=\"How to Do an SEO Competitor Analysis [The Easy Way]\">analyze your competitors</a>. Simply enter your competitor’s URL and the tool will give you a report. You can use this to determine their strengths and weaknesses, and it helps you identify gaps in their strategy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-4-optinmonster\">4. <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"OptinMonster - Lead Generation & Conversion Optimization Tool\" rel=\"noopener\">OptinMonster</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"313\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/optinmonster-homepage.png\" alt=\"OptinMonster homepage.\" class=\"wp-image-221996\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/optinmonster-homepage.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/optinmonster-homepage-300x134.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/optinmonster-homepage-600x268.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/optinmonster-homepage-135x60.png 135w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/optinmonster-homepage-202x90.png 202w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"OptinMonster - Lead Generation & Conversion Optimization Tool\" rel=\"noopener\">OptinMonster</a> is another WordPress plugin that tops many of the best SEO marketing tools lists. It’s a very capable conversion rate optimization (CRO) plugin to help you grow your subscriber and customer base.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>OptinMonster is loved by over 1 million websites because it makes it easy to create stunning opt-in campaigns using popups, floating bars, fullscreen welcome mats, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you run an eCommerce store, you can also use OptinMonster’s robust customization options to reduce cart abandonment, increase sales, grow your email list, and more. That’s because OptinMonster is perfect for creating highly targeted offers. For example, you can show your site visitors popups based on the items in your customer’s cart, a blog post they’re on, and much more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, with OptinMonster’s drag-and-drop builder, creating eye-catching popups that can help grow your business is easy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to use your website as a lead-generation machine, OptinMonster is one of the best SEO marketing tools in this department.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $9/month (billed annually).</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-5-semrush\">5. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Semrush\">Semrush</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"413\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/seo-audit-tools-semrush.png\" alt=\"Semrush is one of the best SEO marketing tools.\" class=\"wp-image-320167\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/seo-audit-tools-semrush.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/seo-audit-tools-semrush-300x176.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/seo-audit-tools-semrush-600x353.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Semrush\">Semrush</a> is another top-ranking SEO marketing tool to consider for your business. It’s a full-suite digital marketing tool that’s loved by many marketers. Some of its most popular use cases include keyword research, search intent analysis, backlink analysis, competitor research and more. Semrush also has a writing assistant to help speed up your content creation. It also has many other <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-content-optimization-tools-for-seo/\" title=\"8 Best Content Optimization Tools for SEO\">content optimization tools</a> to help you nail on-page SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>An advanced feature you’ll love is the Site Audit tool. It reports on domain-level and page-level SEO performance, so you know exactly how your campaigns are performing. The tool also runs technical SEO audits, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/check-competitors-keywords/\" title=\"How to Check and “Steal” Your Competitors’ Top Keywords\">analyzes your competitor’s SEO strategy</a>, analyzes any domain\'s backlink profile, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With so many features and use cases, Semrush certainly deserves a spot among the best SEO marketing tools on the market.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $119.95. A free plan is available, but it’s limited.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-6-monsterinsights\">6. <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MonsterInsights - WordPress Analytics Plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"410\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-monsterinsights-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-163398\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-monsterinsights-2.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-monsterinsights-2-300x175.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-monsterinsights-2-600x350.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-monsterinsights-2-103x60.png 103w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-monsterinsights-2-154x90.png 154w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MonsterInsights - WordPress Analytics Plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">MonsterInsights</a> is the best SEO marketing tool for tracking your site’s analytics. It’s the most popular WordPress Google Analytics plugin on the market, boasting over 3 million users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One reason MonsterInsights has such a large fanbase is because of the intuitive and easy-to-use interface. MonsterInsights gives you all the power of Google Analytics but with a more user-friendly interface.That means you get all the data you need to run a successful site, that data is conveniently placed in your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The plugin gives you deep insights into how visitors interact with your website and helps you track where your site visitors come from and their behavior. This gives you vital insights into what your visitors want and how you can best optimize your site and content for maximum conversions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you use <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/woocommerce/\" title=\"WooCommerce\">WooCommerce</a> or <a href=\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Easy Digital Downloads - WordPress eCommerce plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">Easy Digital Downloads</a> to sell on your website, MonsterInsights also offers enhanced eCommerce tracking features. These help you to optimize your site and landing pages for improved sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $99.50/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-7-affiliatewp\">7. <a href=\"https://affiliatewp.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"AffiliateWP - WordPress Affiliate Management Plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">AffiliateWP</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://affiliatewp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"326\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/affiliatewp-homepage-.png\" alt=\"AffiliateWP homepage\" class=\"wp-image-222405\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/affiliatewp-homepage-.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/affiliatewp-homepage--300x139.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/affiliatewp-homepage--600x279.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/affiliatewp-homepage--129x60.png 129w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/affiliatewp-homepage--194x90.png 194w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Affiliate programs are a great way to spread to leverage word-of-mouth-marketing to boost brand awareness and sales. That’s why every brand should consider running affiliate programs. And one of the best SEO marketing tools to help you do that is <a href=\"https://affiliatewp.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"AffiliateWP - WordPress Affiliate Management Plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">AffiliateWP</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With AffiliateWP, you can transform your WordPress site into a thriving business by building an army of marketers to help sell your products. This powerful plugin allows you to, among other things:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Allows you to easily track your affiliates</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Provides tools to grow your affiliate network and campaigns</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Enables you to manage your affiliate’s payouts</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Setting up an affiliate program is super easy with AffiliateWP, even without technical or coding knowledge. For example, it takes a few clicks to add new affiliates, approve registrations, and edit affiliate accounts. All this can be done from the backend of your website.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>AffiliateWP also offers a default affiliate area page where your affiliates can track their performance and earnings. Plus, once your affiliates have made some sales, you can pay them right from your WordPress dashboard.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $149.50.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-8-ahrefs\">8. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Ahrefs\">Ahrefs</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs.png\" alt=\"Ahrefs homepage\" class=\"wp-image-163411\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs-300x148.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs-600x296.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs-122x60.png 122w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs-183x90.png 183w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Ahrefs\">Ahrefs</a> is another comprehensive digital marketing and SEO toolkit with some in-built SEO marketing tools. Some of the most common ones are the Site Explorer and the Keyword Explorer. These are great for competitor research and developing a comprehensive SEO content strategy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ahrefs also has a fantastic SEO audit tool you can use to uncover your site’s technical and on-page SEO issues. The tool crawls all your website\'s pages and provides a report with your overall SEO health score. It also visualizes critical data in easy-to-understand charts, flags all possible SEO issues, and recommends how to fix them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>These, and more modules make Ahrefs one of the most powerful SEO marketing tools to help you boost your traffic and revenue.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $99.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-9-pushengage\">9. <a href=\"https://pushengage.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"PushEngage - Best Web Push Notification Software\" rel=\"noopener\">PushEngage</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://pushengage.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"795\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pushengage-site-aio.png\" alt=\"PushEngage homepage\" class=\"wp-image-52452\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pushengage-site-aio.png 795w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pushengage-site-aio-300x159.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pushengage-site-aio-768x408.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pushengage-site-aio-600x318.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pushengage-site-aio-113x60.png 113w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/pushengage-site-aio-170x90.png 170w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://pushengage.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"PushEngage - Best Web Push Notification Software\" rel=\"noopener\">PushEngage</a> is one of the best push notification software on the market. The plugin sends popup notifications straight to users’ desktop and mobile browsers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Push notifications are alerts or messages sent from websites to browsers that show up for those who have signed up. They can be used to notify subscribers of important updates, messages, promotions, or events from your brand.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is why PushEngage is one of the best SEO marketing tools you can include in your toolbox. Web push notifications can help you attract visitors back to your site, giving you more opportunities to convert them.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Setting up push notifications with PushEngage is easy. It also has automation functionalities, so you can automate the process of sending push notifications. For greater engagement, you can even set it to send them in the recipient\'s time zone.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best part about using a plugin like PushEngage is that you can communicate with your website visitors even if they haven’t subscribed to your email list. That way, it becomes easier to convert your site visitors into leads.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $9/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-10-trustpulse\">10. <a href=\"https://trustpulse.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"TrustPulse - Social Proof Software to Grow Conversions\" rel=\"noopener\">TrustPulse</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://pushengage.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"391\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trustpulse-homepage.png\" alt=\"TrustPulse home page.\" class=\"wp-image-221993\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trustpulse-homepage.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trustpulse-homepage-300x167.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trustpulse-homepage-600x334.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trustpulse-homepage-108x60.png 108w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/trustpulse-homepage-162x90.png 162w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://trustpulse.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"TrustPulse - Social Proof Software to Grow Conversions\" rel=\"noopener\">TrustPulse</a> stands out as the best SEO marketing tool for demonstrating social proof. It’s a FOMO (fear of missing out) and social proof plugin that shows notifications to your visitors as they browse your website. These include user engagement, purchases, popular products, signups, and more. The notifications are designed to help gain your visitors\' trust and create a sense of urgency, encouraging your site visitors to take action.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Don’t worry. It may sound complicated, but you don’t need any technical knowledge to get TrustPulse running on your site. Once installed, the plugin will automatically track user activity on your site and use this data to create personalized popups. All you have to do is customize the notification text and select the data you want to display to visitors.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides on-site notifications, TrustPulse also enables you to create action messages. These prompt site visitors to take certain actions as they browse your site. Examples include clicking on a popup to sign up, reading a particular blog post, and more.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ultimately, TrustPulse is an SEO marketing tool that helps you gain visitors’ trust through social proof. As a result, your conversion rates will soar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $5/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-11-funnelkit-formerly-woofunnels\">11. <a href=\"https://funnelkit.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"FunnelKit\">FunnelKit (formerly WooFunnels)</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://funnelkit.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/best-woocommerce-plugins-funnelkit.png\" alt=\"FunnelKit home page\" class=\"wp-image-185881\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/best-woocommerce-plugins-funnelkit.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/best-woocommerce-plugins-funnelkit-300x182.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/best-woocommerce-plugins-funnelkit-600x364.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/best-woocommerce-plugins-funnelkit-99x60.png 99w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/best-woocommerce-plugins-funnelkit-148x90.png 148w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://funnelkit.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"FunnelKit\">FunnelKit</a> is a powerful sales funnel builder. It lets you create high-converting checkout pages, abandoned cart recovery, one-click upsells, and various other automations to help boost profits.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because these are essential to sales and marketing, FunnelKit deserves a prominent position on any list of the best SEO marketing tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of FunnelKit’s biggest advantages is that it’s super easy to use—no code or technical knowledge is required. For fast deployment, the plugin comes with customizable templates to help you get started. You can also create reusable workflows to help you launch subsequent marketing funnels and automations faster.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, FunnelKit has a built-in split testing function that helps you optimize your campaigns for maximum impact. You can easily A/B test elements like campaign copy, headlines, CTAs, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>FunnelKit is undoubtedly one of the best SEO marketing tools for brands that want to grow revenue through optimized sales funnels and marketing automation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $99.50 per year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-12-google-search-console\">12. <a href=\"https://search.google.com/search-console/about\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Google Search Console\">Google Search Console</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://search.google.com/search-console/about\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"244\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Google-Search-Console.png\" alt=\"Google Search Console home page.\" class=\"wp-image-45640\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Google-Search-Console.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Google-Search-Console-300x105.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Google-Search-Console-600x209.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Google-Search-Console-172x60.png 172w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Google-Search-Console-258x90.png 258w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://search.google.com/search-console/about\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Google Search Console\">Google Search Console</a> (GSC) is a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-free-seo-tools/\" title=\"21 Best Free SEO Tools to Boost Your Rankings\">free SEO marketing tool</a> by Google. It allows you to track your site’s performance and identify technical issues impacting it. You can also use it to monitor your keyword rankings, impressions, clickthrough rates, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, one of GSC\'s biggest drawbacks is that the reports can contain so much data that they can be overwhelming for beginners. This is one of the main reasons we recommend using AIOSEO’s Search Statistics instead. And if you want more in-depth data, MonsterInsights gives you the same data as GSC (and a little extra) but presented in an easy-to-understand format.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One reason SEOs love GSC is that you can use it to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-submit-a-sitemap-to-google-wordpress-tutorial/\" title=\"How to Submit a Sitemap to Google (WordPress Tutorial)\">submit sitemaps</a> for faster crawling of content. This improves your chances of ranking high on search engines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-13-instagram-feed-pro\">13. <a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/instagram-feed\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Smash Balloon Instagram Feed plugin for WordPress\" rel=\"noopener\">Instagram Feed Pro</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/instagram-feed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/SmashBalloon-Instagram-Feed-Pro.png\" alt=\"Instagram Feed Pro by SmashBalloon.\" class=\"wp-image-268791\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/SmashBalloon-Instagram-Feed-Pro.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/SmashBalloon-Instagram-Feed-Pro-300x214.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/SmashBalloon-Instagram-Feed-Pro-600x427.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/instagram-feed\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Smash Balloon Instagram Feed plugin for WordPress\" rel=\"noopener\">Instagram Feed Pro</a> by Smash Balloon is the SEO marketing tool for running Instagram campaigns. It’s a popular WordPress plugin for displaying Instagram photos on your site. It’s highly customizable and easy to manage, even for absolute beginners.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The plugin even lets you display Instagram posts from multiple Instagram accounts in the same or different feeds. You can also create multiple Instagram feeds on the same page and customize the style to match your brand.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To grow your Instagram following, the plugin enables you to add a ‘Follow on Instagram’ button to your feed. Social Photo Feed plugin allows you to customize your feeds and display photos in thumbnail, medium, or full size. Other than that, you can add a beautiful header at the top of your feed to display your photos in random or chronological order, just the way you want.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re looking for the best SEO marketing tool to help boost your social media campaigns, Social Photo Feed is it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: free. Paid plans start at $49</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-14-google-trends\">14. <a href=\"https://trends.google.com/trends/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Google Trends\">Google Trends</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://trends.google.com/trends/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"541\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-marketing-tools-google-trends-1024x541.png\" alt=\"Google Trends home page.\" class=\"wp-image-365488\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-marketing-tools-google-trends-1024x541.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-marketing-tools-google-trends-300x158.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-marketing-tools-google-trends-768x406.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-marketing-tools-google-trends-600x317.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-marketing-tools-google-trends.png 1102w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://trends.google.com/trends/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Google Trends\">Google Trends</a> is an invaluable SEO marketing tool that provides insights into the popularity and search volume trends of specific keywords and topics over time. You can use it to gauge whether a particular topic or keyword is worth pursuing based on current trends. Because of this, you can use it for SEO tasks such as keyword research and content ideation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the marketing side, Google Trends can be used to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-do-an-seo-competitor-analysis/\" title=\"How to Do an SEO Competitor Analysis [The Easy Way]\">analyze competitors</a> and check the seasonality of your keywords. These are crucial elements of building a solid marketing strategy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To effectively utilize Google Trends for SEO marketing, you should combine the insights gained from the tool with other SEO practices. By incorporating Google Trends data into your overall SEO strategy, you can better understand user behavior, identify emerging trends, and create more relevant and engaging content that resonates with your target audience.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-15-easy-digital-downloads-edd\">15. <a href=\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Easy Digital Downloads - WordPress eCommerce plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">Easy Digital Downloads</a> (EDD)</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"333\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/best-wordpress-product-review-plugins-edd.png\" alt=\"Easy Digital Downloads home page.\" class=\"wp-image-204943\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/best-wordpress-product-review-plugins-edd.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/best-wordpress-product-review-plugins-edd-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/best-wordpress-product-review-plugins-edd-600x285.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/best-wordpress-product-review-plugins-edd-126x60.png 126w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/best-wordpress-product-review-plugins-edd-190x90.png 190w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://easydigitaldownloads.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Easy Digital Downloads - WordPress eCommerce plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">Easy Digital Downloads</a> (EDD) is the best solution for selling digital products on your website. You don\'t even have to set up an eCommerce store! It’s undoubtedly the best SEO tool for you if you sell digital products like ebooks, plugins, PDFs, software, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To help you increase sales, EDD is packed with many eCommerce and reporting features to help you optimize your marketing campaigns to drive traffic and boost conversions. With a fully integrated shopping cart system, the plugin lets you easily add cart elements to your product pages. Plus, you can create customer account pages where users can view their purchase history, license keys, downloads, and much more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>EDD integrates seamlessly with payment gateways like Stripe, PayPal, Google Pay, Apple Pay, and others, making payment acceptance super easy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free. Paid plans start at $99.50.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-16-facebook-social-post-feed\">16. <a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/custom-facebook-feed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Smash Balloon Facebook Feed plugin for WordPress\">Facebook Feed Pro</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/custom-facebook-feed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"522\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/facebook-feed-pro.png\" alt=\"Facebook Feed Pro home page.\" class=\"wp-image-365496\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/facebook-feed-pro.png 1000w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/facebook-feed-pro-300x157.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/facebook-feed-pro-768x401.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/facebook-feed-pro-600x313.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/custom-facebook-feed\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Smash Balloon Facebook Feed plugin for WordPress\" rel=\"noopener\">Facebook Feed Pro</a> is the best SEO marketing tool for displaying Facebook posts on your site. It makes it easy to display Facebook posts from pages and groups on your WordPress website. Plus, you can match it with your theme so it appears as part of your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The free version of the plugin allows you to display text and links from Facebook posts. If you want to showcase photos, videos, and comments, then you need to upgrade to the premium version of the plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By default, the Facebook feed will adopt the styles of your WordPress theme. However, if you want to change this, the tool gives you full customization options. You can use the visual feed customizer, which has many options to customize every part of your Facebook posts and feed.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If your target audience uses Facebook, then the best SEO marketing tool for your social media campaigns is Social Post Feed.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: free. Paid plans start at $49</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-17-thrive-leads\">17. <a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/leads\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Thrive Leads - WordPress Popup Plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">Thrive Leads</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/leads\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"330\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/thrive-leads-homepage.png\" alt=\"Thrive Leads is one of the best SEO marketing tools in the lead gen department.\" class=\"wp-image-221995\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/thrive-leads-homepage.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/thrive-leads-homepage-300x141.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/thrive-leads-homepage-600x282.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/thrive-leads-homepage-128x60.png 128w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/thrive-leads-homepage-191x90.png 191w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/leads\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Thrive Leads - WordPress Popup Plugin\" rel=\"noopener\">Thrive Leads</a> is the best SEO marketing tool for growing your email list. The <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-a-plugin-beginners-guide-to-wordpress-plugins/\" title=\"What is a Plugin? The Beginner’s Guide to WordPress Plugins\">WordPress plugin</a> comes with various opt-in forms, including 2-step opt-ins, lightbox forms, slide-in forms, and more. This makes it super easy to capture leads on your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides helping grow your list, Thrive Leads also has conversion rate optimization (CRO) tools. It offers powerful features like lead groups, which allow you to segment your list based on specific criteria. You also get A/B testing tools, dynamic text replacement for personalization, and much more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to grow your email list fast, Thrive Leads is the best SEO marketing tool for the job.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $99/year. You can also get the complete ThriveSuite (5 plugin bundle) for $299/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-18-exploding-topics\">18. <a href=\"https://explodingtopics.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Exploding Topics\">Exploding Topics</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://explodingtopics.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"557\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-marketing-tools-exploding-topics.png\" alt=\"Exploding Topics home page.\" class=\"wp-image-365499\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-marketing-tools-exploding-topics.png 900w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-marketing-tools-exploding-topics-300x186.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/seo-marketing-tools-explo