ree.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-21-feeds-for-youtube\">21. <a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/youtube-feed\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Smash Balloon YouTube Feed plugin for WordPress\" rel=\"noopener\">Feeds for YouTube</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/youtube-feed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"900\" height=\"518\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/youtube-feed-pro.png\" alt=\"YouTube Feed Pro home page.\" class=\"wp-image-365507\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/youtube-feed-pro.png 900w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/youtube-feed-pro-300x173.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/youtube-feed-pro-768x442.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/youtube-feed-pro-600x345.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/youtube-feed\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Smash Balloon YouTube Feed plugin for WordPress\" rel=\"noopener\">YouTube Feed Pro</a> is the best WordPress plugin for displaying YouTube videos on your website. This makes it a fantastic SEO marketing tool if your target audience prefers to consume content in video format.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>By default, the plugin matches the style of your WordPress theme. However, you can customize it and change the look and feel of how your videos are displayed. It also offers multiple options for displaying YouTube videos, including gallery, list, and grid layouts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best part about the plugin is that you can also create multiple feeds from different YouTube channels. You can also add a ‘Load More’ button to indefinitely load YouTube videos on your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: free. Paid plans start at $49</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-22-advanced-coupons\">22. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/advanced-coupon-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Advanced Coupons\">Advanced Coupons</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/advanced-coupon-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-woocommerce-plugins-advanced-coupons.png\" alt=\"Advanced Coupons home page.\" class=\"wp-image-179322\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-woocommerce-plugins-advanced-coupons.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-woocommerce-plugins-advanced-coupons-300x145.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-woocommerce-plugins-advanced-coupons-600x290.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-woocommerce-plugins-advanced-coupons-124x60.png 124w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/best-woocommerce-plugins-advanced-coupons-186x90.png 186w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you run a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/woocommerce/\">WooCommerce store</a>, one of the best SEO marketing tools you can leverage is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/advanced-coupon-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"20 Best WooCommerce Plugins for Your Store [2024 Edition]\">Advanced Coupons</a>. This powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-woocommerce-plugins/\" title=\"20 Best WooCommerce Plugins for Your Store [2024 Edition]\">WooCommerce plugin</a> takes your coupon marketing game to the next level, thereby helping you drive more sales.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Advanced Coupons was designed to help you build and deploy impactful promotions that result in exceptional sales. While WooCommerce has a default coupon feature, it’s pretty basic and lacks some essential functions. Advanced Coupons, however, adds some spice to your coupon experience. For example, you can schedule your vouchers, automatically add a coupon when certain cart conditions are met, and much more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides creating irresistible coupons and loyalty programs, Advanced Coupons has a reporting dashboard that gives you important campaign metrics. This is undoubtedly one plugin to install if you want to boost your sales and grow your WooCommerce store traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $39.50/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-23-easy-affiliate\">23. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/easy-affiliate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Easy Affiliate\">Easy Affiliate</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/easy-affiliate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"364\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/easyaffiliate-homepage.png\" alt=\"Easy Affiliate home page\" class=\"wp-image-221286\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/easyaffiliate-homepage.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/easyaffiliate-homepage-300x156.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/easyaffiliate-homepage-600x311.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/easyaffiliate-homepage-116x60.png 116w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/easyaffiliate-homepage-174x90.png 174w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/easy-affiliate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Easy Affiliate\">Easy Affiliate</a> is another WordPress plugin to consider when looking for the best SEO marketing tools. The plugin enables you to create a self-hosted affiliate program on your WordPress site.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Easy Affiliate installed, you can view several different reports. Examples include transactions, overall stats for your affiliates, a list of your top affiliates, the clicks coming in, and even how much each affiliate has earned. All this right from your WordPress dashboard. This data is easy to digest as it’s presented visually in graphs and charts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>True to its name, signing up affiliates is easy as Easy Affiliate has a built-in affiliate application process. Those who qualify to be part of your affiliate program can access the Affiliate Dashboard to edit account information, monitor their stats, download links and banners, and much more. Plus, the plugin integrates with most payment gateways and comes with shopping cart integration. All this makes it easier for your affiliates to accept and process payments.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $99.50/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-24-pretty-links\">24. <a href=\"https://prettylinks.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Pretty Links\">Pretty Links</a>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/prettylinkpro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"680\" height=\"327\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/pretty-links.png\" alt=\"Pretty Links home page\" class=\"wp-image-268842\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/pretty-links.png 680w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/pretty-links-300x144.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/pretty-links-600x289.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/refer/prettylinkpro/\"></a>If you run an affiliate marketing site, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/prettylinkpro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Pretty Links\">Pretty Links</a> is another WordPress plugin you should install on your site. It’s one of the best link management plugins for WordPress, allowing you to manage affiliate links easily. The best part is it shortens your affiliate links, making them user-friendly and memorable. This makes it easier for people to interact with your content and share your links.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides aesthetics, Pretty Links also has powerful link tracking capabilities. This makes it a must-have tool for businesses that rely on tracking their links. This includes affiliate marketers, podcasters, bloggers, and anyone else who wants to create short URLs in WordPress easily.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All this makes Pretty Links an essential SEO marketing tool for driving affiliate sales.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $99.50/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-25-thirstyaffiliates\">25. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"ThirstyAffiliates\">ThirstyAffiliates</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"326\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/thirsty-affiliates.png\" alt=\"Thirsty Affiliates Home Page\" class=\"wp-image-268840\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/thirsty-affiliates.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/thirsty-affiliates-300x140.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/thirsty-affiliates-600x279.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Another link management tool that should be on your radar is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/thirstyaffiliates/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"ThirstyAffiliates\">ThirstyAffiliates</a>. ThirstyAffiliates is a powerful plugin that can help you:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Cloak long, ugly affiliate links</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Protect your commissions</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Easily insert affiliate links into blog posts and other content</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>One feature that stands out is Auto Linking. Once you provide keywords for anchor text, the tool automatically adds affiliate links to your content. Another is the 404 Checker, a tool that crawls your site and proactively checks your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-easily-find-and-fix-404-errors-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Easily Find and Fix 404 Errors in WordPress\">404 errors</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to these, ThirstyAffiliates\'s ease of use is undoubtedly one of the best SEO marketing tools for affiliate marketers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $79.50/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-seo-marketing-tools-your-faqs-answered\">SEO Marketing Tools: Your FAQs Answered</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-are-seo-marketing-tools\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What are SEO Marketing Tools?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>SEO marketing tools are software applications designed to assist businesses in optimizing their websites for better search engine visibility, traffic, and revenue generation. These tools provide a wide range of features, including keyword research, on-page optimization, link building, site auditing, competitor analysis, and much more.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-are-the-different-types-of-seo-marketing-tools\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What are the different types of SEO marketing tools? </h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>SEO marketing tools can be categorized into various types, including keyword research tools, on-page optimization tools, link building tools, site auditing tools, rank-tracking tools, and competitor analysis tools. Many comprehensive SEO platforms offer a combination of these features.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-are-the-best-seo-marketing-tools\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What are the best SEO marketing tools?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>The best SEO marketing tool for search visibility is All In One SEO (AIOSEO). Other tools include WPForms for capturing visitor information, MonsterInsights for analytics, and Semrush for keyword research and content planning.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-best-seo-marketing-tools-our-top-picks\">Best SEO Marketing Tools: Our Top Picks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this article has helped you discover the best SEO marketing tools. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our guide to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-mistakes-every-small-business-should-avoid/\" title=\"8 SEO Mistakes Every Small Business Should Avoid\">common SEO mistakes to avoid</a> or our list of the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-local-seo-tools/\" title=\"7 Best Local SEO Tools to Help Boost Your Rankings\">best local SEO tools</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-marketing-tools/\">20+ Best SEO Marketing Tools to Drive Traffic and Revenue in 2024</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0