temaps. Its advanced features give you granular control over sitemap settings.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $59/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-5-yoast-seo\">5. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Yoast SEO\">Yoast SEO</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1002\" height=\"589\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/yoast-home-page.png\" alt=\"Yoast SEO home page\" class=\"wp-image-359982\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/yoast-home-page.png 1002w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/yoast-home-page-300x176.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/yoast-home-page-768x451.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/yoast-home-page-600x353.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Yoast SEO\">Yoast SEO</a> is another popular WordPress SEO plugin designed to help users optimize their sites to rank high in search results. The plugin also features a basic sitemap generator. It automatically creates XML sitemaps and integrates with search engines for easy submission.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yoast SEO also provides options to customize your sitemap settings, such as priority and change frequency. It also automatically removes content you mark as noindex from the sitemap.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s a detailed comparison of <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/yoast-vs-rank-math-vs-all-in-one-seo/\" title=\"Yoast vs Rank Math vs All in One SEO: Which Is Better?\">Yoast vs. Rank Math vs. AIOSEO</a> to help you see which is the clear winner.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: $99/year for the core plugin. Addons are purchased separately.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-6-simple-sitemap\">6. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-sitemap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Simple Sitemap\">Simple Sitemap</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-sitemap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1002\" height=\"513\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-simple-sitemap.png\" alt=\"Simple Sitemap home page\" class=\"wp-image-359983\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-simple-sitemap.png 1002w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-simple-sitemap-300x154.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-simple-sitemap-768x393.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-simple-sitemap-600x307.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-sitemap/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Simple Sitemap\">Simple Sitemap</a> is the most popular HTML sitemap generator for WordPress sites. One reason for that is it’s easy to use. It’s a simple tool that makes building and previewing your sitemap visually in the post editor easy!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Simple Sitemap, there’s no need to use confusing and complicated code to create your HTML sitemap. You also don’t have to swap back and forth between the editor and front end to ensure your HTML sitemap displays correctly. The plugin works seamlessly within the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/gutenberg-block-plugins/\" title=\"17 Best Gutenberg Blocks Plugins for 2024\">Gutenberg editor</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For advanced users, Simple Sitemap supports shortcodes, giving you more control over how your HTML sitemap will look.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-7-companion-sitemap-generator\">7. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/companion-sitemap-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Companion Sitemap Generator\">Companion Sitemap Generator</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/companion-sitemap-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1002\" height=\"449\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-companion-sitemap-generator.png\" alt=\"Companion Sitemap Generator home page\" class=\"wp-image-359986\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-companion-sitemap-generator.png 1002w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-companion-sitemap-generator-300x134.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-companion-sitemap-generator-768x344.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-companion-sitemap-generator-600x269.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/companion-sitemap-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Companion Sitemap Generator\">Companion Sitemap Generator</a> is a free WordPress plugin that helps you create both XML and HTML sitemaps. This makes it a versatile option for users looking to improve their site\'s discoverability and navigation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The XML sitemap functionality provides some basic customization options. For example, you can adjust the update frequency for pages and selectively include or exclude certain pages from the sitemap.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, the standout feature of Companion Sitemap Generator is its built-in HTML sitemap functionality. This allows you to easily generate a user-friendly, hierarchical listing of your site\'s pages and posts, making it simpler for visitors to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/breadcrumb-navigation-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Easily Add Breadcrumb Navigation in WordPress\">navigate your content</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Overall, Companion Sitemap Generator is a well-rounded sitemap solution that caters to the needs of WordPress users who want to improve their search engine optimization and user experience by implementing both XML and HTML sitemaps.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-8-google-xml-sitemaps\">8. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-sitemap-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Google XML Sitemaps\">Google XML Sitemaps</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-sitemap-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"902\" height=\"511\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-xml-sitemap-generator-for-google.png\" alt=\"XML sitemap generator for Google\" class=\"wp-image-360003\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-xml-sitemap-generator-for-google.png 902w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-xml-sitemap-generator-for-google-300x170.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-xml-sitemap-generator-for-google-768x435.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/best-sitemap-generator-xml-sitemap-generator-for-google-600x340.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-sitemap-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Google XML sitemaps\">Google XML Sitemaps</a> is one of the best sitemap generators for WordPress regarding dedicated plugins. It has been around for years, has amassed a large user base, and has fantastic reviews from users in the WordPress community.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A notable feature of this plugin is its support for multiple languages, making it a viable option for <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/the-beginners-guide-to-wordpress-multilingual-seo/\" title=\"The Beginner’s Guide to WordPress Multilingual SEO\">multilingual SEO</a>. It also offers compatibility with WordPress multisite installations, allowing site owners with multiple sites under a single WordPress network to manage their sitemaps efficiently.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another powerful aspect of this plugin is its extensive filtering system, which allows other <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-plugins/\" title=\"32 Best WordPress Plugins in 2024 [Paid and Free]\">WordPress plugins</a> to contribute their pages to the sitemap. This ensures that the generated XML sitemap includes a comprehensive list of all the content on your website, including post types, taxonomies, and custom post types.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Overall, the Google XML Sitemaps plugin is a long-standing and feature-rich option for WordPress users who want to create and manage high-quality XML sitemaps for their sites.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-the-best-sitemap-generator-our-top-picks\">The Best Sitemap Generator: Our Top Picks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our top pick for the best sitemap generator is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"All in One SEO - WordPress SEO Plugin and Toolkit\" rel=\"noopener\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO). The plugin offers unparalleled flexibility and customization options for optimizing sitemaps. Other top picks are <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/jetpack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Jetpack\">Jetpack</a> and <a href=\"https://www.xml-sitemaps.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"XML Sitemaps\">XML Sitemaps</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"aioseo-best-sitemap-generator-your-faqs-answered\">Best Sitemap Generator: Your FAQs Answered</h2>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-what-is-a-sitemap\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What is a Sitemap?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>A sitemap is a file, typically in XML or HTML format, that provides a structured list of all the pages, posts, and other content on your WordPress site.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-do-i-really-need-a-sitemap-for-my-wordpress-site\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">Do I really need a sitemap for my WordPress site?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>Yes, a sitemap is highly recommended for all WordPress websites, regardless of size or complexity. Sitemaps help search engines better understand and index your website\'s content, improving visibility and higher rankings.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-whats-the-difference-between-an-xml-sitemap-and-an-html-sitemap\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">What\'s the difference between an XML sitemap and an HTML sitemap?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>XML sitemaps are machine-readable files that provide a structured list of your website\'s URLs and metadata like change frequency and priority. Search engines primarily use them to crawl and index your content. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>HTML sitemaps, on the other hand, are human-readable pages that offer a visual representation of your website\'s structure, making it easier for visitors to navigate your content.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div data-schema-only=\"false\" class=\"wp-block-aioseo-faq\" id=\"aioseo-how-do-i-generate-a-sitemap\"><h3 class=\"aioseo-faq-block-question\">How do I generate a sitemap?</h3><div class=\"aioseo-faq-block-answer\">\n<p>The easiest way to generate a sitemap is by using a plugin like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"All in One SEO - WordPress SEO Plugin and Toolkit\" rel=\"noopener\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO). It’s a powerful WordPress plugin that also offers a flexible and feature-rich sitemap generator.</p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you find the best sitemap generator for your site. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like how to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-submit-a-sitemap-to-google-wordpress-tutorial/\" title=\"How to Submit a Sitemap to Google (WordPress Tutorial)\">submit your sitemap to Google</a> or, alternatively, how to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-submit-a-sitemap-to-bing-wordpress-tutorial/\" title=\"How to Submit a Sitemap to Bing (WordPress Tutorial)\">submit your sitemap to Bing</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">X (Twitter)</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.&nbsp;</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-sitemap-generators/\">The Best Sitemap Generator: 8 Top Picks for 2024 [Paid and Free]</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://aioseo.com/best-sitemap-generators/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\"