(131, 1, '2024-08-28 01:27:20', '2024-08-28 01:27:20', '<!-- wp:image {\"id\":113,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://loamsllc.online/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Screenshot_20240810_174933_WhatsApp-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-113\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Hello,</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>This is Loams, LLC an online data production, management and distribution system.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Current project is focused on Lotto game numbers. Today, the games are operating below full capacity. For example, the Mega Millions lotto is operating below 4% capacity without any assurances. Loams, LLC system will operate at 100% capacity every time.</strong>&nbsp;<strong>The system is designed to maximizes lotto games utility. Loams, LLC guarantees every user at least one prize win in any draw. The system is unique, universal and one-of-a-kind. You cannot find similar system or guarantees anywhere else in the world.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Users will receive strings (Units/Rows) of unique Lotto game sets of numbers ranging between 20 and 30 sets each and then play these numbers at any retail store or online. Each string sets of numbers is unique and costs $1. Use the link below to order your unique winning sets of numbers. Please specify order name you are interested in…Mega Millions (1 string = 25 sets), Power Ball (1 string = 26 sets), Cash 4 Life (1 string = 24 sets), California Super-Lotto Plus (1 string = 27 sets), Georgia Jumbo Bucks (1 string = 23 sets) or Michigan Lotto 47 (1 string = 23 sets). One order at a time. Now offering GA Jumbo Bucks and MI Lotto 47. User must be at least 21 years of Age to participate.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Once you pay, your numbers will be delivered to you. Loams, LLC will pay you $100 for any duplicate sets of numbers that you find or if you do not win at least one prize. The system is designed to raise millionaires every week. It could be you.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>If you have any questions, please email, text or call 202-705-0687/ooadiele@gmail.com.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Give it a try today!</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://checkout.square.site/merchant/MLB3ZT92RH9CF/checkout/YT5F2AL3AC34B42A642QJ5ZD\">https://checkout.square.site/merchant/MLB3ZT92RH9CF/checkout/YT5F2AL3AC34B42A642QJ5ZD</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->', 'LOAMS, LLC SYSTEM PROMOTIONS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '112-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-08-28 01:27:20', '2024-08-28 01:27:20', '', 112, 'https://loamsllc.online/?p=131', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
